1
00:00:00,980 --> 00:00:03,956
<Default><b>[melancholy music]</b></Default>

2
00:00:03,980 --> 00:00:05,426
<Default><b>♪♪</b></Default>

3
00:00:05,450 --> 00:00:07,876
<Default><b>[TRASH] Thank you.
This is for me?</b></Default>

4
00:00:07,900 --> 00:00:09,136
<Default><b>[FOHL] Sure is.</b></Default>

5
00:00:09,160 --> 00:00:11,480
<Default><b>Atla and I made it
for you this morning.</b></Default>

6
00:00:14,080 --> 00:00:15,650
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

7
00:00:16,859 --> 00:00:18,206
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

8
00:00:18,230 --> 00:00:20,309
<Default><b>I sincerely hope
you'll enjoy it.</b></Default>

9
00:00:22,890 --> 00:00:24,809
<Default><b>[murmurs]</b></Default>

10
00:00:25,829 --> 00:00:27,835
<Default><b>Hold
on, could this be...</b></Default>

11
00:00:27,859 --> 00:00:29,675
<Default><b>Mom used to make this.</b></Default>

12
00:00:29,699 --> 00:00:31,465
<Default><b>Brother told me.</b></Default>

13
00:00:31,489 --> 00:00:32,889
<Default><b>[exhales deeply]</b></Default>

14
00:00:34,159 --> 00:00:36,296
<Default><b>It's not too
salty, is it?</b></Default>

15
00:00:36,320 --> 00:00:38,939
<Default><b>No it's fine, really.
[chuckles]</b></Default>

16
00:00:40,789 --> 00:00:42,866
<Default><b>It's so good.</b></Default>

17
00:00:42,890 --> 00:00:44,305
<Default><b>Very good.</b></Default>

18
00:00:44,329 --> 00:00:46,735
<Default><b>It's wonderful.</b></Default>

19
00:00:46,759 --> 00:00:49,536
<Default><b>[MIRELLIA] Trash's little
sister is named Lucia.</b></Default>

20
00:00:49,560 --> 00:00:52,926
<Default><b>Turns out her children
are Fohl and Atla.</b></Default>

21
00:00:52,950 --> 00:00:55,830
<Default><b>If that's the case, shouldn't
we tell the two of them?</b></Default>

22
00:00:57,409 --> 00:00:59,375
<Default><b>Trash is happy
with how it is.</b></Default>

23
00:00:59,399 --> 00:01:02,146
<Default><b>Changes could possibly
disrupt things.</b></Default>

24
00:01:02,170 --> 00:01:03,986
<Default><b>Anyway, how
was Siltvelt?</b></Default>

25
00:01:04,010 --> 00:01:07,006
<Default><b>I'm told you may have
faced some trouble there.</b></Default>

26
00:01:07,030 --> 00:01:10,575
<Default><b>Everything happened exactly
the way you said it would.</b></Default>

27
00:01:10,599 --> 00:01:13,105
<Default><b>Well, it sounds like
things worked out in the end</b></Default>

28
00:01:13,129 --> 00:01:15,286
<Default><b>because thanks to you</b></Default>

29
00:01:15,310 --> 00:01:18,116
<Default><b>are going to be helping
in the war against the Phoenix.</b></Default>

30
00:01:18,140 --> 00:01:20,605
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] You wasted
no time setting that up.</b></Default>

31
00:01:20,629 --> 00:01:22,456
<Default><b>[MIRELLIA] Preparing
for the battle with the Phoenix</b></Default>

32
00:01:22,480 --> 00:01:24,896
<Default><b>is the number one
priority right now.</b></Default>

33
00:01:24,920 --> 00:01:27,465
<Default><b>So what's next
for you, Shield Hero?</b></Default>

34
00:01:27,489 --> 00:01:29,846
<Default><b>I'll continue preparing
for the Phoenix.</b></Default>

35
00:01:29,870 --> 00:01:33,075
<Default><b>But first, I have to settle
things with Q'ten Lo.</b></Default>

36
00:01:33,099 --> 00:01:35,486
<Default><b>I can't focus on what's
in front of us</b></Default>

37
00:01:35,510 --> 00:01:37,825
<Default><b>if I'm worrying
about another attack.</b></Default>

38
00:01:37,849 --> 00:01:39,555
<Default><b>Then do as you wish.</b></Default>

39
00:01:39,579 --> 00:01:40,786
<Default><b>Oh, and Raphtalia.</b></Default>

40
00:01:40,810 --> 00:01:42,036
<Default><b>Yes?</b></Default>

41
00:01:42,060 --> 00:01:43,976
<Default><b>[MIRELLIA]
Depending on how things go</b></Default>

42
00:01:44,000 --> 00:01:46,185
<Default><b>the next time we
meet, I may very well</b></Default>

43
00:01:46,209 --> 00:01:48,089
<Default><b>be welcoming
you as royalty.</b></Default>

44
00:01:49,030 --> 00:01:50,126
<Default><b>[RAPHTALIA]
I'm sorry.</b></Default>

45
00:01:50,150 --> 00:01:52,045
<Default><b>I know this is
an important time.</b></Default>

46
00:01:52,069 --> 00:01:54,465
<Default><b>It's not your fault
Q'ten Lo attacked.</b></Default>

47
00:01:54,489 --> 00:01:57,200
<Default><b>And I'm just doing
my job as any Lord would.</b></Default>

48
00:01:58,629 --> 00:02:00,385
<Default><b>Master Naofumi.</b></Default>

49
00:02:00,409 --> 00:02:02,766
<Default><b>What did he think
of your home cooking?</b></Default>

50
00:02:02,790 --> 00:02:04,626
<Default><b>Go ahead and see
for yourself.</b></Default>

51
00:02:04,650 --> 00:02:06,926
<Default><b>I only wish
we made more.</b></Default>

52
00:02:06,950 --> 00:02:08,556
<Default><b>If you're finished
with things here</b></Default>

53
00:02:08,580 --> 00:02:09,996
<Default><b>then we should
get back home.</b></Default>

54
00:02:10,020 --> 00:02:11,746
<Default><b>As soon as we're ready</b></Default>

55
00:02:11,770 --> 00:02:13,010
<Default><b>[ALL] Right!</b></Default>

56
00:02:15,460 --> 00:02:18,145
<Default><b>[theme music]</b></Default>

57
00:02:18,169 --> 00:02:21,306
<Default><b>♪♪</b></Default>

58
00:02:21,330 --> 00:02:22,307
<Default><b>♪ Hey ♪</b></Default>

59
00:02:22,331 --> 00:02:24,295
<Default><b>THE RISING OF
THE SHIELD HERO</b></Default>

60
00:02:24,319 --> 00:02:26,855
<Default><b>♪ Nothing standing
in our way right now ♪</b></Default>

61
00:02:26,879 --> 00:02:32,545
<Default><b>[singing in Japanese]</b></Default>

62
00:02:32,569 --> 00:02:35,195
<Default><b>♪ The reason that I choose
to fight when I travel ♪</b></Default>

63
00:02:35,219 --> 00:02:38,735
<Default><b>♪ Proof that I exist ♪</b></Default>

64
00:02:38,759 --> 00:02:40,515
<Default><b>[singing in Japanese]</b></Default>

65
00:02:40,539 --> 00:02:41,885
<Default><b>♪ Live with no regrets ♪</b></Default>

66
00:02:41,909 --> 00:02:44,876
<Default><b>♪ It seems like
a never-ending genocide ♪</b></Default>

67
00:02:44,900 --> 00:02:46,235
<Default><b>♪ What's the way
to becoming ♪</b></Default>

68
00:02:46,259 --> 00:02:48,605
<Default><b>♪♪</b></Default>

69
00:02:48,629 --> 00:02:50,526
<Default><b>♪ The choice is yours ♪</b></Default>

70
00:02:50,550 --> 00:02:53,436
<Default><b>♪ If the pieces
of your story cross ♪</b></Default>

71
00:02:53,460 --> 00:02:56,096
<Default><b>♪ Don't let them go
Don't let them go ♪</b></Default>

72
00:02:56,120 --> 00:02:59,365
<Default><b>♪ Cause you
don't want me</b></Default>

73
00:02:59,389 --> 00:03:03,256
<Default><b>♪ No limit to
where we go ♪</b></Default>

74
00:03:03,280 --> 00:03:06,836
<Default><b>♪ I will protect
your resolution ♪</b></Default>

75
00:03:06,860 --> 00:03:09,226
<Default><b>♪ No matter
what comes next ♪</b></Default>

76
00:03:09,250 --> 00:03:12,705
<Default><b>♪ Cause every time again</b></Default>

77
00:03:12,729 --> 00:03:14,906
<Default><b>♪ We'll never
lose and cry ♪</b></Default>

78
00:03:14,930 --> 00:03:18,445
<Default><b>♪ Now nobody can
stop us, no way ♪</b></Default>

79
00:03:18,469 --> 00:03:20,545
<Default><b>♪ We'll back
you every time ♪</b></Default>

80
00:03:20,569 --> 00:03:22,846
<Default><b>♪ It was just pushing
through the flame to some ♪</b></Default>

81
00:03:22,870 --> 00:03:24,376
<Default><b>♪ That we
can stake out ♪</b></Default>

82
00:03:24,400 --> 00:03:27,586
<Default><b>♪ Even if there's no
end to this road ♪</b></Default>

83
00:03:27,610 --> 00:03:31,545
<Default><b>♪ We protect
our resolution ♪</b></Default>

84
00:03:31,569 --> 00:03:32,955
<Default><b>♪ Yeah ♪</b></Default>

85
00:03:32,979 --> 00:03:35,066
<Default><b>♪ No need
for hesitation ♪</b></Default>

86
00:03:35,090 --> 00:03:37,695
<Default><b>♪ Nothing standing
in our way right now ♪</b></Default>

87
00:03:37,719 --> 00:03:38,696
<Default><b>♪ Hey ♪</b></Default>

88
00:03:38,720 --> 00:03:40,936
<Default><b>♪ No need
for hesitation ♪</b></Default>

89
00:03:40,960 --> 00:03:44,000
<Default><b>[singing in Japanese]
♪ go now ♪</b></Default>

90
00:03:45,939 --> 00:03:48,165
<Default><b>EPISODE 6: LEAVING PORT</b></Default>

91
00:03:48,189 --> 00:03:50,509
<Default><b>[RATOTILLE] My goodness</b></Default>

92
00:03:52,310 --> 00:03:53,596
<Default><b>Why are you back?</b></Default>

93
00:03:53,620 --> 00:03:56,246
<Default><b>To choose who's going
to Q'ten Lo with me.</b></Default>

94
00:03:56,270 --> 00:03:57,825
<Default><b>Are you taking these?</b></Default>

95
00:03:57,849 --> 00:03:59,306
<Default><b>Thanks to everyone
in the village</b></Default>

96
00:03:59,330 --> 00:04:00,686
<Default><b>they're super
strong now.</b></Default>

97
00:04:00,710 --> 00:04:04,276
<Default><b>Hmm. I want as much fighting
power as I can get.</b></Default>

98
00:04:04,300 --> 00:04:07,276
<Default><b>But we have to be able
to defend the village, too.</b></Default>

99
00:04:07,300 --> 00:04:09,526
<Default><b>It'd be good to have
Sadeena with us.</b></Default>

100
00:04:09,550 --> 00:04:11,075
<Default><b>She knows the area.</b></Default>

101
00:04:11,099 --> 00:04:12,496
<Default><b>Hm, that's true.</b></Default>

102
00:04:12,520 --> 00:04:15,096
<Default><b>I'd forgotten about that.
Who else?</b></Default>

103
00:04:15,120 --> 00:04:17,505
<Default><b>[RAPHTALIA] We could bring
Atla and Fohl as well.</b></Default>

104
00:04:17,529 --> 00:04:19,846
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] They did help out
a lot back in Siltvelt.</b></Default>

105
00:04:19,870 --> 00:04:23,055
<Default><b>By the way</b></Default>

106
00:04:23,079 --> 00:04:26,026
<Default><b>They're out training</b></Default>

107
00:04:26,050 --> 00:04:28,576
<Default><b>Even if the curse is still
affecting both of them</b></Default>

108
00:04:28,600 --> 00:04:30,915
<Default><b>it doesn't mean that
they're not cardinal heroes.</b></Default>

109
00:04:30,939 --> 00:04:32,355
<Default><b>At least one of them
should come along.</b></Default>

110
00:04:32,379 --> 00:04:33,906
<Default><b>[SADEENA]
If you're going to Q'ten Lo</b></Default>

111
00:04:33,930 --> 00:04:35,425
<Default><b>you should
take him as well.</b></Default>

112
00:04:35,449 --> 00:04:36,896
<Default><b>But why Gaelion?</b></Default>

113
00:04:36,920 --> 00:04:40,396
<Default><b>You may not know, but
Q'ten Lo has a Water Dragon.</b></Default>

114
00:04:40,420 --> 00:04:42,456
<Default><b>As a fellow dragon</b></Default>

115
00:04:42,480 --> 00:04:45,235
<Default><b>be able to sense him before
he poses any sort of threat.</b></Default>

116
00:04:45,259 --> 00:04:46,236
<Default><b>Yeah!</b></Default>

117
00:04:46,260 --> 00:04:47,295
<Default><b>Sure.</b></Default>

118
00:04:47,319 --> 00:04:48,346
<Default><b>Let's bring him.</b></Default>

119
00:04:48,370 --> 00:04:49,906
<Default><b>[WYNDIA] No fair!</b></Default>

120
00:04:49,930 --> 00:04:51,315
<Default><b>I wanna go!</b></Default>

121
00:04:51,339 --> 00:04:53,139
<Default><b>I can fight
too, you know?</b></Default>

122
00:04:54,420 --> 00:04:56,795
<Default><b>Do you remember what happened
when the village was attacked?</b></Default>

123
00:04:56,819 --> 00:04:58,136
<Default><b>Mm.</b></Default>

124
00:04:58,160 --> 00:05:00,216
<Default><b>We don't know if or when
they'll come back.</b></Default>

125
00:05:00,240 --> 00:05:03,565
<Default><b>Making sure everyone here is
safe is really important, too.</b></Default>

126
00:05:03,589 --> 00:05:04,836
<Default><b>You up for it?</b></Default>

127
00:05:04,860 --> 00:05:05,860
<Default><b>Mm.</b></Default>

128
00:05:07,250 --> 00:05:08,305
<Default><b>Now, then...</b></Default>

129
00:05:08,329 --> 00:05:10,545
<Default><b>[ERHARD]
Hello? Anyone in there?</b></Default>

130
00:05:10,569 --> 00:05:11,569
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

131
00:05:12,009 --> 00:05:13,076
<Default><b>Hey.</b></Default>

132
00:05:13,100 --> 00:05:14,375
<Default><b>What is it, Erhard?</b></Default>

133
00:05:14,399 --> 00:05:18,026
<Default><b>Room for one more
on your trip to Q'ten Lo?</b></Default>

134
00:05:18,050 --> 00:05:20,125
<Default><b>I went ahead and took
a good look at the weapons</b></Default>

135
00:05:20,149 --> 00:05:21,956
<Default><b>those guys were using.</b></Default>

136
00:05:21,980 --> 00:05:25,656
<Default><b>And if I'm not mistaken</b></Default>

137
00:05:25,680 --> 00:05:26,786
<Default><b>Are you positive?</b></Default>

138
00:05:26,810 --> 00:05:28,946
<Default><b>Yeah, that's how
it seemed to me.</b></Default>

139
00:05:28,970 --> 00:05:31,675
<Default><b>They've been
missing for ages</b></Default>

140
00:05:31,699 --> 00:05:33,156
<Default><b>to finally find them.</b></Default>

141
00:05:33,180 --> 00:05:34,580
<Default><b>I'm begging you.</b></Default>

142
00:05:35,839 --> 00:05:37,836
<Default><b>It's bound to be
dangerous there.</b></Default>

143
00:05:37,860 --> 00:05:39,036
<Default><b>Sure you wanna go?</b></Default>

144
00:05:39,060 --> 00:05:40,925
<Default><b>I was an adventurer</b></Default>

145
00:05:40,949 --> 00:05:43,505
<Default><b>My level is 87</b></Default>

146
00:05:43,529 --> 00:05:44,735
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
Wait, seriously?</b></Default>

147
00:05:44,759 --> 00:05:46,016
<Default><b>[ERHARD]
Take me along with you</b></Default>

148
00:05:46,040 --> 00:05:48,115
<Default><b>and I'll keep
your weapons maintained.</b></Default>

149
00:05:48,139 --> 00:05:49,116
<Default><b>All right, fine.</b></Default>

150
00:05:49,140 --> 00:05:50,125
<Default><b>You can join us then.</b></Default>

151
00:05:50,149 --> 00:05:51,315
<Default><b>You won't regret it.</b></Default>

152
00:05:51,339 --> 00:05:52,485
<Default><b>[laughs]</b></Default>

153
00:05:52,509 --> 00:05:53,966
<Default><b>[chuckles]
That explains why he was</b></Default>

154
00:05:53,990 --> 00:05:56,435
<Default><b>so proficient
with a sword.</b></Default>

155
00:05:56,459 --> 00:05:58,906
<Default><b>Him being able to train
you makes sense now.</b></Default>

156
00:05:58,930 --> 00:06:02,235
<Default><b>Anyway, we'll discuss the rest
when Itsuki and Ren get back.</b></Default>

157
00:06:02,259 --> 00:06:03,966
<Default><b>If possible, I'd like
to leave tomorrow.</b></Default>

158
00:06:03,990 --> 00:06:04,966
<Default><b>[KEEL] Big sis!</b></Default>

159
00:06:04,990 --> 00:06:05,967
<Default><b>[ALL] Huh?</b></Default>

160
00:06:05,991 --> 00:06:07,471
<Default><b>You gotta help me!</b></Default>

161
00:06:08,910 --> 00:06:11,146
<Default><b>Why in the world are
you dressed like that?</b></Default>

162
00:06:11,170 --> 00:06:13,865
<Default><b>Those two made
me wear this.</b></Default>

163
00:06:13,889 --> 00:06:15,846
<Default><b>A cross-dresser, huh?</b></Default>

164
00:06:15,870 --> 00:06:17,956
<Default><b>I don't know
if you can say that</b></Default>

165
00:06:17,980 --> 00:06:20,196
<Default><b>especially since
Keel's actually a girl.</b></Default>

166
00:06:20,220 --> 00:06:21,555
<Default><b>[ALL gasps]</b></Default>

167
00:06:21,579 --> 00:06:23,815
<Default><b>I found out when we were
taking measurements</b></Default>

168
00:06:23,839 --> 00:06:25,276
<Default><b>for her to work
at the shop.</b></Default>

169
00:06:25,300 --> 00:06:27,156
<Default><b>I just always
thought I was a guy</b></Default>

170
00:06:27,180 --> 00:06:28,276
<Default><b>so I never
questioned it.</b></Default>

171
00:06:28,300 --> 00:06:29,476
<Default><b>Yeah, same here.</b></Default>

172
00:06:29,500 --> 00:06:31,846
<Default><b>But why that outfit
in particular?</b></Default>

173
00:06:31,870 --> 00:06:34,206
<Default><b>She was creatively
inspired, she says.</b></Default>

174
00:06:34,230 --> 00:06:36,875
<Default><b>Not to mention
everybody loved it.</b></Default>

175
00:06:36,899 --> 00:06:38,346
<Default><b>[KEEL]
Well, I hate it.</b></Default>

176
00:06:38,370 --> 00:06:39,347
<Default><b>All right.</b></Default>

177
00:06:39,371 --> 00:06:40,505
<Default><b>Master Naofumi?</b></Default>

178
00:06:40,529 --> 00:06:42,545
<Default><b>Keel, from now on</b></Default>

179
00:06:42,569 --> 00:06:43,615
<Default><b>that when
you go trading.</b></Default>

180
00:06:43,639 --> 00:06:44,735
<Default><b>[shrieks]</b></Default>

181
00:06:44,759 --> 00:06:46,086
<Default><b>The more
attention you get</b></Default>

182
00:06:46,110 --> 00:06:47,505
<Default><b>the more sales
you'll make.</b></Default>

183
00:06:47,529 --> 00:06:49,995
<Default><b>Use that talent of yours.
Don't waste it.</b></Default>

184
00:06:50,019 --> 00:06:52,935
<Default><b>I want to be
a strong man</b></Default>

185
00:06:52,959 --> 00:06:54,076
<Default><b>Forget about gender.</b></Default>

186
00:06:54,100 --> 00:06:55,826
<Default><b>You have to be useful.</b></Default>

187
00:06:55,850 --> 00:06:57,656
<Default><b>Understood?</b></Default>

188
00:06:57,680 --> 00:07:00,266
<Default><b>All right, if
you say so.</b></Default>

189
00:07:00,290 --> 00:07:03,516
<Default><b>Master Naofumi, you've got
money symbols in your eyes.</b></Default>

190
00:07:03,540 --> 00:07:06,540
<Default><b>[ERHARD] It's nice to know
that some things never change.</b></Default>

191
00:07:08,839 --> 00:07:10,555
<Default><b>[MELTY] Naofumi!</b></Default>

192
00:07:10,579 --> 00:07:12,276
<Default><b>It looks like
you've returned, huh?</b></Default>

193
00:07:12,300 --> 00:07:13,576
<Default><b>How'd it go?</b></Default>

194
00:07:13,600 --> 00:07:15,586
<Default><b>I heard you ran
into trouble in Siltvelt.</b></Default>

195
00:07:15,610 --> 00:07:17,266
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
To put it lightly.</b></Default>

196
00:07:17,290 --> 00:07:20,016
<Default><b>Did anything of note happen in
the village while I was away?</b></Default>

197
00:07:20,040 --> 00:07:22,505
<Default><b>Well, we haven't had to deal
with any more assassins</b></Default>

198
00:07:22,529 --> 00:07:25,855
<Default><b>but we did find
explosion craters nearby.</b></Default>

199
00:07:25,879 --> 00:07:28,415
<Default><b>They might have tried
to set a trap for us.</b></Default>

200
00:07:28,439 --> 00:07:32,185
<Default><b>Either that or they got
in a fight with someone.</b></Default>

201
00:07:32,209 --> 00:07:34,079
<Default><b>The real
question is who?</b></Default>

202
00:07:35,509 --> 00:07:38,485
<Default><b>[eerie music]</b></Default>

203
00:07:38,509 --> 00:07:44,065
<Default><b>♪♪</b></Default>

204
00:07:44,089 --> 00:07:45,625
<Default><b>[MOTOYASU]
Found you, villains!</b></Default>

205
00:07:45,649 --> 00:07:47,045
<Default><b>[MONKEY ASSASSIN]
Who's there?</b></Default>

206
00:07:47,069 --> 00:07:48,966
<Default><b>[adventurous music]</b></Default>

207
00:07:48,990 --> 00:07:50,976
<Default><b>Your nightmare!</b></Default>

208
00:07:51,000 --> 00:07:52,930
<Default><b>[explosion]</b></Default>

209
00:07:54,379 --> 00:07:55,855
<Default><b>[grumbles]</b></Default>

210
00:07:55,879 --> 00:07:59,776
<Default><b>Ahh. My spear didn't work
as well as it should have.</b></Default>

211
00:07:59,800 --> 00:08:01,605
<Default><b>No matter.</b></Default>

212
00:08:01,629 --> 00:08:04,136
<Default><b>As source of thy
power, I order thee</b></Default>

213
00:08:04,160 --> 00:08:07,375
<Default><b>decipher the laws
of nature and burn my foes</b></Default>

214
00:08:07,399 --> 00:08:09,526
<Default><b>until only ash remains.</b></Default>

215
00:08:09,550 --> 00:08:11,755
<Default><b>Drifa Firestorm!</b></Default>

216
00:08:11,779 --> 00:08:13,389
<Default><b>[explosion]</b></Default>

217
00:08:14,389 --> 00:08:15,959
<Default><b>[yelling]</b></Default>

218
00:08:16,959 --> 00:08:18,990
<Default><b>Filth must be
cleansed by fire.</b></Default>

219
00:08:20,439 --> 00:08:22,370
<Default><b>Now, on to the next one.</b></Default>

220
00:08:24,759 --> 00:08:27,055
<Default><b>[ITSUKI] We really don't
know what to make of it.</b></Default>

221
00:08:27,079 --> 00:08:29,599
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] I'll look
into it when I have time.</b></Default>

222
00:08:29,769 --> 00:08:31,966
<Default><b>[MELTY] Hey, Naofumi.
[NAOFUMI] What is it?</b></Default>

223
00:08:31,990 --> 00:08:34,946
<Default><b>I know that you've been
busy lately, but don't forget</b></Default>

224
00:08:34,970 --> 00:08:37,196
<Default><b>you need to do what
Fitoria asked you.</b></Default>

225
00:08:37,220 --> 00:08:39,716
<Default><b>I will, once we're done
with things in Q'ten Lo.</b></Default>

226
00:08:39,740 --> 00:08:42,865
<Default><b>And just remember, she gave
you the reward in advance.</b></Default>

227
00:08:42,889 --> 00:08:43,966
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] I know.</b></Default>

228
00:08:43,990 --> 00:08:45,235
<Default><b>- [FILO] Melty!
- Huh?</b></Default>

229
00:08:45,259 --> 00:08:46,236
<Default><b>I'll be there
in a second.</b></Default>

230
00:08:46,260 --> 00:08:48,735
<Default><b>It's time to play.</b></Default>

231
00:08:48,759 --> 00:08:50,696
<Default><b>[MELTY]
I wasn't done talking.</b></Default>

232
00:08:50,720 --> 00:08:52,265
<Default><b>Fitoria, huh?</b></Default>

233
00:08:52,289 --> 00:08:55,686
<Default><b>She said she wanted the four
heroes to get closer, but...</b></Default>

234
00:08:55,710 --> 00:09:00,155
<Default><b>Sir Ren, is there anything
missing from the shopping list?</b></Default>

235
00:09:00,179 --> 00:09:02,235
<Default><b>How about adding
some dried jerky?</b></Default>

236
00:09:02,259 --> 00:09:03,365
<Default><b>We're running low.</b></Default>

237
00:09:03,389 --> 00:09:04,366
<Default><b>Will do.</b></Default>

238
00:09:04,390 --> 00:09:06,306
<Default><b>Thank you so much.</b></Default>

239
00:09:06,330 --> 00:09:08,235
<Default><b>Looks like you've
been helping out.</b></Default>

240
00:09:08,259 --> 00:09:11,375
<Default><b>It's not much, but I'm
doing everything I can.</b></Default>

241
00:09:11,399 --> 00:09:13,716
<Default><b>I am a part of this
village, after all.</b></Default>

242
00:09:13,740 --> 00:09:16,385
<Default><b>Naofumi, do you think we
should come along to help</b></Default>

243
00:09:16,409 --> 00:09:17,836
<Default><b>you guys fight
in Q'ten Lo?</b></Default>

244
00:09:17,860 --> 00:09:19,365
<Default><b>It's hard to say.</b></Default>

245
00:09:19,389 --> 00:09:21,785
<Default><b>I honestly don't know
if the Cardinal Weapons</b></Default>

246
00:09:21,809 --> 00:09:23,916
<Default><b>will even work on them.</b></Default>

247
00:09:23,940 --> 00:09:25,836
<Default><b>But we're taking
a ship to get there.</b></Default>

248
00:09:25,860 --> 00:09:27,826
<Default><b>If we have to fight
a battle at sea</b></Default>

249
00:09:27,850 --> 00:09:30,336
<Default><b>long-range weapons
will definitely help.</b></Default>

250
00:09:30,360 --> 00:09:33,196
<Default><b>Itsuki, Rishia</b></Default>

251
00:09:33,220 --> 00:09:34,476
<Default><b>Absolutely.</b></Default>

252
00:09:34,500 --> 00:09:37,275
<Default><b>[squeals] I'll
do my best.</b></Default>

253
00:09:37,299 --> 00:09:40,875
<Default><b>But I want you
staying here</b></Default>

254
00:09:40,899 --> 00:09:43,635
<Default><b>Are you up for protecting
the village with Eclair?</b></Default>

255
00:09:43,659 --> 00:09:44,985
<Default><b>Sure, but...</b></Default>

256
00:09:45,009 --> 00:09:46,275
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] I only ask
because it seems</b></Default>

257
00:09:46,299 --> 00:09:48,336
<Default><b>like the villagers
trust you.</b></Default>

258
00:09:48,360 --> 00:09:50,926
<Default><b>For now, just focus
on breaking the curse.</b></Default>

259
00:09:50,950 --> 00:09:53,255
<Default><b>I'll call you with
the portal when we need you.</b></Default>

260
00:09:53,279 --> 00:09:54,719
<Default><b>Yeah, you got it.</b></Default>

261
00:09:57,950 --> 00:09:59,365
<Default><b>[knock on door]</b></Default>

262
00:09:59,389 --> 00:10:00,875
<Default><b>[RAPHTALIA]
Um, Master Naofumi.</b></Default>

263
00:10:00,899 --> 00:10:02,485
<Default><b>Hmm?</b></Default>

264
00:10:02,509 --> 00:10:06,145
<Default><b>The emperor, who
exactly are they?</b></Default>

265
00:10:06,169 --> 00:10:08,186
<Default><b>What kind of person
sends assassins</b></Default>

266
00:10:08,210 --> 00:10:10,615
<Default><b>to protect
their position?</b></Default>

267
00:10:10,639 --> 00:10:13,355
<Default><b>It's human nature
to try and cling to power.</b></Default>

268
00:10:13,379 --> 00:10:15,635
<Default><b>So they're no different
from anyone else.</b></Default>

269
00:10:15,659 --> 00:10:19,076
<Default><b>I have no interest
in those things, though.</b></Default>

270
00:10:19,100 --> 00:10:20,255
<Default><b>Don't tell me.</b></Default>

271
00:10:20,279 --> 00:10:22,976
<Default><b>Tell it to the people
of Q'ten Lo.</b></Default>

272
00:10:23,000 --> 00:10:24,466
<Default><b>Right.</b></Default>

273
00:10:24,490 --> 00:10:26,645
<Default><b>I have my doubts
they'll be convinced</b></Default>

274
00:10:26,669 --> 00:10:28,360
<Default><b>but we have to try.</b></Default>

275
00:10:32,870 --> 00:10:35,066
<Default><b>[folk music]</b></Default>

276
00:10:35,090 --> 00:10:38,350
<Default><b>[chattering]</b></Default>

277
00:10:41,480 --> 00:10:43,765
<Default><b>Has everything I
requested been prepared?</b></Default>

278
00:10:43,789 --> 00:10:44,789
<Default><b>Yes.</b></Default>

279
00:10:45,769 --> 00:10:47,615
<Default><b>Everything's
almost on board.</b></Default>

280
00:10:47,639 --> 00:10:50,706
<Default><b>The last 10% is
being loaded now.</b></Default>

281
00:10:50,730 --> 00:10:52,905
<Default><b>[RISHIA]
All of this is just 10%</b></Default>

282
00:10:52,929 --> 00:10:54,346
<Default><b>of what we're
bringing along?</b></Default>

283
00:10:54,370 --> 00:10:56,245
<Default><b>Well, we can't
have anything happening</b></Default>

284
00:10:56,269 --> 00:10:58,066
<Default><b>to the Shield
Hero, can we?</b></Default>

285
00:10:58,090 --> 00:11:01,775
<Default><b>So we went ahead and added
a little bit extra.</b></Default>

286
00:11:01,799 --> 00:11:02,946
<Default><b>Incredible.</b></Default>

287
00:11:02,970 --> 00:11:05,976
<Default><b>That's so kind
of you to do that.</b></Default>

288
00:11:06,000 --> 00:11:09,529
<Default><b>Am I mistaken, or do they
not seem happy to see me?</b></Default>

289
00:11:10,950 --> 00:11:13,416
<Default><b>[RISHIA]
No, I think you're right.</b></Default>

290
00:11:13,440 --> 00:11:14,905
<Default><b>[grumbles]</b></Default>

291
00:11:14,929 --> 00:11:16,895
<Default><b>[yelps]</b></Default>

292
00:11:16,919 --> 00:11:19,596
<Default><b>OK, it's time to board.</b></Default>

293
00:11:19,620 --> 00:11:22,836
<Default><b>When everything's
loaded, we're leaving.</b></Default>

294
00:11:22,860 --> 00:11:25,420
<Default><b>[MAKINA] I have some
troubling news to report.</b></Default>

295
00:11:26,309 --> 00:11:29,285
<Default><b>Only just a few moments
ago, the false emperor</b></Default>

296
00:11:29,309 --> 00:11:31,476
<Default><b>left port for
our nation.</b></Default>

297
00:11:31,500 --> 00:11:33,576
<Default><b>But there's no
need to worry.</b></Default>

298
00:11:33,600 --> 00:11:36,015
<Default><b>They'll never make
it to our lands.</b></Default>

299
00:11:36,039 --> 00:11:39,166
<Default><b>You have my word that they'll
perish at sea before then.</b></Default>

300
00:11:39,190 --> 00:11:42,346
<Default><b>You just leave the dirty
work to me and me alone.</b></Default>

301
00:11:42,370 --> 00:11:44,946
<Default><b>Someone with a kind
heart such as yourself</b></Default>

302
00:11:44,970 --> 00:11:46,806
<Default><b>shouldn't have
to worry about staining</b></Default>

303
00:11:46,830 --> 00:11:48,495
<Default><b>their hands with blood.</b></Default>

304
00:11:48,519 --> 00:11:50,476
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

305
00:11:50,500 --> 00:11:52,956
<Default><b>[adventurous music]</b></Default>

306
00:11:52,980 --> 00:11:55,436
<Default><b>[boat whooshing]</b></Default>

307
00:11:55,460 --> 00:11:57,875
<Default><b>♪♪</b></Default>

308
00:11:57,899 --> 00:11:58,956
<Default><b>[RAPHY]
Whoo-hee!</b></Default>

309
00:11:58,980 --> 00:12:00,806
<Default><b>[FILO]
It's like we're flying!</b></Default>

310
00:12:00,830 --> 00:12:01,895
<Default><b>Hey, don't do that.</b></Default>

311
00:12:01,919 --> 00:12:02,896
<Default><b>It's bad luck.</b></Default>

312
00:12:02,920 --> 00:12:04,966
<Default><b>♪♪</b></Default>

313
00:12:04,990 --> 00:12:07,889
<Default><b>[retches]</b></Default>

314
00:12:09,830 --> 00:12:11,615
<Default><b>That's a strange
light, isn't it?</b></Default>

315
00:12:11,639 --> 00:12:12,826
<Default><b>Yeah, it sure is.</b></Default>

316
00:12:12,850 --> 00:12:14,946
<Default><b>But we can't reach
Q'ten Lo without it.</b></Default>

317
00:12:14,970 --> 00:12:16,115
<Default><b>Look there!</b></Default>

318
00:12:16,139 --> 00:12:18,985
<Default><b>♪♪</b></Default>

319
00:12:19,009 --> 00:12:20,696
<Default><b>Are those whirlpools?</b></Default>

320
00:12:20,720 --> 00:12:22,745
<Default><b>If you don't keep
following the light</b></Default>

321
00:12:22,769 --> 00:12:25,255
<Default><b>the whirlpools will
block your path.</b></Default>

322
00:12:25,279 --> 00:12:28,436
<Default><b>We've got a whirlpool
right in front of us.</b></Default>

323
00:12:28,460 --> 00:12:29,916
<Default><b>Hard to starboard!</b></Default>

324
00:12:29,940 --> 00:12:31,625
<Default><b>Hard to starboard!</b></Default>

325
00:12:31,649 --> 00:12:34,139
<Default><b>[creaking, whooshing]</b></Default>

326
00:12:35,590 --> 00:12:36,590
<Default><b>Whee!</b></Default>

327
00:12:39,250 --> 00:12:41,635
<Default><b>♪♪</b></Default>

328
00:12:41,659 --> 00:12:43,765
<Default><b>Your parents
and Raphtalia's parents</b></Default>

329
00:12:43,789 --> 00:12:45,336
<Default><b>made it through
these conditions?</b></Default>

330
00:12:45,360 --> 00:12:47,125
<Default><b>That's right.</b></Default>

331
00:12:47,149 --> 00:12:50,000
<Default><b>My mother and father
did this, just like us.</b></Default>

332
00:12:52,840 --> 00:12:55,405
<Default><b>These whirlpools
are a headache.</b></Default>

333
00:12:55,429 --> 00:12:58,966
<Default><b>Yeah. Why do you think
your master went to Q'ten Lo</b></Default>

334
00:12:58,990 --> 00:13:00,196
<Default><b>in the first place?</b></Default>

335
00:13:00,220 --> 00:13:01,735
<Default><b>No idea.</b></Default>

336
00:13:01,759 --> 00:13:03,586
<Default><b>He was always
on the move, whether it</b></Default>

337
00:13:03,610 --> 00:13:07,515
<Default><b>meant chasing skirts or running
from debt collectors.</b></Default>

338
00:13:07,539 --> 00:13:09,145
<Default><b>He sounds like a loser.</b></Default>

339
00:13:09,169 --> 00:13:11,025
<Default><b>[ERHARD]
He has a lot of problems</b></Default>

340
00:13:11,049 --> 00:13:13,316
<Default><b>but also
top-notch skills.</b></Default>

341
00:13:13,340 --> 00:13:16,405
<Default><b>After falling in love with one
of his weapons at first sight</b></Default>

342
00:13:16,429 --> 00:13:17,716
<Default><b>I started
learning from him.</b></Default>

343
00:13:17,740 --> 00:13:18,836
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
That good, huh?</b></Default>

344
00:13:18,860 --> 00:13:20,395
<Default><b>[ERHARD]
If I can meet him again</b></Default>

345
00:13:20,419 --> 00:13:23,176
<Default><b>I can take my skills
to the next level.</b></Default>

346
00:13:23,200 --> 00:13:25,436
<Default><b>If he's as talented
as you say</b></Default>

347
00:13:25,460 --> 00:13:27,505
<Default><b>maybe I should just
hire him instead.</b></Default>

348
00:13:27,529 --> 00:13:29,416
<Default><b>Come on, don't
be like that.</b></Default>

349
00:13:29,440 --> 00:13:30,946
<Default><b>[laughter]</b></Default>

350
00:13:30,970 --> 00:13:34,546
<Default><b>[squawks]</b></Default>

351
00:13:34,570 --> 00:13:36,525
<Default><b>Anything to report?</b></Default>

352
00:13:36,549 --> 00:13:39,015
<Default><b>I'm not able to see
it, but I can sense</b></Default>

353
00:13:39,039 --> 00:13:41,186
<Default><b>a dragon in
the far distance.</b></Default>

354
00:13:41,210 --> 00:13:42,666
<Default><b>Let me guess</b></Default>

355
00:13:42,690 --> 00:13:46,275
<Default><b>Hmm. I tried to get
closer to see</b></Default>

356
00:13:46,299 --> 00:13:48,296
<Default><b>but I was blocked
by a barrier.</b></Default>

357
00:13:48,320 --> 00:13:50,855
<Default><b>That dragon must
have put it up.</b></Default>

358
00:13:50,879 --> 00:13:53,265
<Default><b>We're almost
to Q'ten Lo's waters.</b></Default>

359
00:13:53,289 --> 00:13:55,086
<Default><b>[panting]</b></Default>

360
00:13:55,110 --> 00:13:56,355
<Default><b>This fog.</b></Default>

361
00:13:56,379 --> 00:13:59,706
<Default><b>I hope we're able
to get there unscathed.</b></Default>

362
00:13:59,730 --> 00:14:01,115
<Default><b>These guys were
willing to come</b></Default>

363
00:14:01,139 --> 00:14:02,655
<Default><b>all the way
to our village.</b></Default>

364
00:14:02,679 --> 00:14:05,056
<Default><b>They won't let us reach
land without a fight.</b></Default>

365
00:14:05,080 --> 00:14:06,820
<Default><b>Stay sharp, everyone.</b></Default>

366
00:14:16,440 --> 00:14:18,350
<Default><b>[water shushing]</b></Default>

367
00:14:19,350 --> 00:14:22,049
<Default><b>Something is approaching
from our rear starboard!</b></Default>

368
00:14:24,659 --> 00:14:27,615
<Default><b>Another ship, it's going
to collide with us!</b></Default>

369
00:14:27,639 --> 00:14:30,096
<Default><b>[bell ringing]</b></Default>

370
00:14:30,120 --> 00:14:32,556
<Default><b>[adventurous music]</b></Default>

371
00:14:32,580 --> 00:14:33,557
<Default><b>[arrows thudding]</b></Default>

372
00:14:33,581 --> 00:14:37,025
<Default><b>[squeals]</b></Default>

373
00:14:37,049 --> 00:14:38,249
<Default><b>Wind Arrow!</b></Default>

374
00:14:40,409 --> 00:14:41,690
<Default><b>[explosion]</b></Default>

375
00:14:42,690 --> 00:14:43,706
<Default><b>Master Naofumi!</b></Default>

376
00:14:43,730 --> 00:14:44,816
<Default><b>Let's go!</b></Default>

377
00:14:44,840 --> 00:14:46,936
<Default><b>Oh, what's
going... [squeals]</b></Default>

378
00:14:46,960 --> 00:14:48,899
<Default><b>[explosion]</b></Default>

379
00:14:50,360 --> 00:14:57,145
<Default><b>♪♪</b></Default>

380
00:14:57,169 --> 00:14:59,110
<Default><b>[arrows thudding]</b></Default>

381
00:15:02,049 --> 00:15:04,216
<Default><b>[MONKEY ASSASSIN] Death
to the false emperor!</b></Default>

382
00:15:04,240 --> 00:15:06,296
<Default><b>Tornado Throw!</b></Default>

383
00:15:06,320 --> 00:15:07,560
<Default><b>Meteor Shot!</b></Default>

384
00:15:08,879 --> 00:15:10,405
<Default><b>[BUNNY ASSASSIN]
Death to the false emperor!</b></Default>

385
00:15:10,429 --> 00:15:11,716
<Default><b>[FOX AND MONKEY ASSASSINS]
Death to the false emperor!</b></Default>

386
00:15:11,740 --> 00:15:12,936
<Default><b>[SADEENA]
I'll handle this.</b></Default>

387
00:15:12,960 --> 00:15:15,296
<Default><b>As source of thy
power, I order thee</b></Default>

388
00:15:15,320 --> 00:15:19,135
<Default><b>decipher the laws of nature
and let the lightning I command</b></Default>

389
00:15:19,159 --> 00:15:20,816
<Default><b>pierce the
foes before me!</b></Default>

390
00:15:20,840 --> 00:15:21,976
<Default><b>All Drifa!</b></Default>

391
00:15:22,000 --> 00:15:24,405
<Default><b>Chain Lightning!</b></Default>

392
00:15:24,429 --> 00:15:28,155
<Default><b>[BUNNY ASSASSIN groans]</b></Default>

393
00:15:28,179 --> 00:15:29,666
<Default><b>Be careful using that.</b></Default>

394
00:15:29,690 --> 00:15:30,890
<Default><b>Zweit Aura!</b></Default>

395
00:15:32,799 --> 00:15:33,775
<Default><b>Good timing.</b></Default>

396
00:15:33,799 --> 00:15:34,776
<Default><b>Thank you.</b></Default>

397
00:15:34,800 --> 00:15:36,316
<Default><b>♪♪</b></Default>

398
00:15:36,340 --> 00:15:38,525
<Default><b>We need to take them
alive and question them.</b></Default>

399
00:15:38,549 --> 00:15:43,275
<Default><b>♪♪</b></Default>

400
00:15:43,299 --> 00:15:44,666
<Default><b>They might
self-destruct.</b></Default>

401
00:15:44,690 --> 00:15:45,916
<Default><b>Take them
out before then.</b></Default>

402
00:15:45,940 --> 00:15:47,635
<Default><b>- Right.
- Roger.</b></Default>

403
00:15:47,659 --> 00:15:48,859
<Default><b>Understood.</b></Default>

404
00:15:50,250 --> 00:15:53,355
<Default><b>Brother, please, we don't have
time for you to be seasick.</b></Default>

405
00:15:53,379 --> 00:15:55,385
<Default><b>Yeah, I know that.</b></Default>

406
00:15:55,409 --> 00:15:57,726
<Default><b>Stardust Blade!</b></Default>

407
00:15:57,750 --> 00:15:59,586
<Default><b>[smack]</b></Default>

408
00:15:59,610 --> 00:16:04,206
<Default><b>Knew it. Hero attacks don't
have an effect on them.</b></Default>

409
00:16:04,230 --> 00:16:06,966
<Default><b>Die, false emperor!</b></Default>

410
00:16:06,990 --> 00:16:08,306
<Default><b>Air Strike Shield!</b></Default>

411
00:16:08,330 --> 00:16:09,330
<Default><b>Raphy!</b></Default>

412
00:16:11,039 --> 00:16:12,806
<Default><b>[whimpers]</b></Default>

413
00:16:12,830 --> 00:16:15,745
<Default><b>[grumbles]</b></Default>

414
00:16:15,769 --> 00:16:17,245
<Default><b>[thud]</b></Default>

415
00:16:17,269 --> 00:16:20,605
<Default><b>[groans]</b></Default>

416
00:16:20,629 --> 00:16:23,446
<Default><b>[shrieks]</b></Default>

417
00:16:23,470 --> 00:16:24,447
<Default><b>[splash]</b></Default>

418
00:16:24,471 --> 00:16:27,735
<Default><b>[explosion]</b></Default>

419
00:16:27,759 --> 00:16:28,745
<Default><b>[splash]</b></Default>

420
00:16:28,769 --> 00:16:30,216
<Default><b>Hey! Wait!</b></Default>

421
00:16:30,240 --> 00:16:33,456
<Default><b>Stop!
You're no good underwater.</b></Default>

422
00:16:33,480 --> 00:16:35,826
<Default><b>Let's push them
back, Gaelion.</b></Default>

423
00:16:35,850 --> 00:16:36,985
<Default><b>Lightning
Strike Harpoon!</b></Default>

424
00:16:37,009 --> 00:16:38,899
<Default><b>[yelling]</b></Default>

425
00:16:39,899 --> 00:16:41,556
<Default><b>OK, we're almost done!</b></Default>

426
00:16:41,580 --> 00:16:43,966
<Default><b>[MONKEY ASSASSIN]
Glory to the almighty emperor!</b></Default>

427
00:16:43,990 --> 00:16:44,966
<Default><b>Crap!</b></Default>

428
00:16:44,990 --> 00:16:46,190
<Default><b>[explosion]</b></Default>

429
00:16:48,309 --> 00:16:49,706
<Default><b>[squeals]</b></Default>

430
00:16:49,730 --> 00:16:51,176
<Default><b>No, you don't.</b></Default>

431
00:16:51,200 --> 00:16:53,676
<Default><b>Shield Prison!</b></Default>

432
00:16:53,700 --> 00:16:56,559
<Default><b>[zapping, crashing]</b></Default>

433
00:16:58,940 --> 00:17:00,379
<Default><b>[thump]</b></Default>

434
00:17:01,820 --> 00:17:03,155
<Default><b>Nice job there.</b></Default>

435
00:17:03,179 --> 00:17:04,216
<Default><b>But are you OK?</b></Default>

436
00:17:04,240 --> 00:17:05,426
<Default><b>Yeah.</b></Default>

437
00:17:05,450 --> 00:17:08,126
<Default><b>We're clear
to starboard and to port.</b></Default>

438
00:17:08,150 --> 00:17:10,795
<Default><b>[ITSUKI] Looks like we
should be OK for now.</b></Default>

439
00:17:10,819 --> 00:17:14,015
<Default><b>As long as we servants
of master Naofumi are here</b></Default>

440
00:17:14,039 --> 00:17:17,095
<Default><b>they'll never stop
us in our tracks.</b></Default>

441
00:17:17,119 --> 00:17:19,255
<Default><b>This one, too, huh?</b></Default>

442
00:17:19,279 --> 00:17:21,575
<Default><b>To think they attacked
with the whirlpools here.</b></Default>

443
00:17:21,599 --> 00:17:25,285
<Default><b>That's how bad they wanted to
stop us from reaching Q'ten Lo.</b></Default>

444
00:17:25,309 --> 00:17:28,795
<Default><b>[SADEENA] I hope we can make it
there without any more trouble.</b></Default>

445
00:17:28,819 --> 00:17:31,309
<Default><b>[rumbling]</b></Default>

446
00:17:32,309 --> 00:17:33,809
<Default><b>[splash]</b></Default>

447
00:17:35,799 --> 00:17:38,775
<Default><b>[dramatic music]</b></Default>

448
00:17:38,799 --> 00:17:42,265
<Default><b>♪♪</b></Default>

449
00:17:42,289 --> 00:17:48,740
<Default><b>[squeals]</b></Default>

450
00:17:49,740 --> 00:17:50,717
<Default><b>Naofumi!</b></Default>

451
00:17:50,741 --> 00:17:52,055
<Default><b>Raphtalia!</b></Default>

452
00:17:52,079 --> 00:17:53,386
<Default><b>[squawks]</b></Default>

453
00:17:53,410 --> 00:17:55,065
<Default><b>Master Naofumi!</b></Default>

454
00:17:55,089 --> 00:17:56,089
<Default><b>Atla!</b></Default>

455
00:17:58,200 --> 00:18:00,180
<Default><b>[explosion]</b></Default>

456
00:18:03,160 --> 00:18:06,116
<Default><b>[intense music]</b></Default>

457
00:18:06,140 --> 00:18:12,089
<Default><b>♪♪</b></Default>

458
00:18:19,809 --> 00:18:23,926
<Default><b>[grunts] Where are we?</b></Default>

459
00:18:23,950 --> 00:18:25,295
<Default><b>Are you OK?</b></Default>

460
00:18:25,319 --> 00:18:26,296
<Default><b>Yes.</b></Default>

461
00:18:26,320 --> 00:18:27,466
<Default><b>Thank goodness.</b></Default>

462
00:18:27,490 --> 00:18:29,015
<Default><b>I found you two!</b></Default>

463
00:18:29,039 --> 00:18:30,335
<Default><b>[meeps]</b></Default>

464
00:18:30,359 --> 00:18:32,376
<Default><b>I guess you got caught
in that thing, too?</b></Default>

465
00:18:32,400 --> 00:18:36,196
<Default><b>Yes. It seems the Water
Dragon's brought us here.</b></Default>

466
00:18:36,220 --> 00:18:39,436
<Default><b>[GAELION] I could feel it
in the whirlpool myself.</b></Default>

467
00:18:39,460 --> 00:18:41,446
<Default><b>The Water Dragon.</b></Default>

468
00:18:41,470 --> 00:18:44,255
<Default><b>Surely there must have been
another way to get us here.</b></Default>

469
00:18:44,279 --> 00:18:45,815
<Default><b>Yeah, you're right.</b></Default>

470
00:18:45,839 --> 00:18:47,799
<Default><b>So why would
they do all this?</b></Default>

471
00:18:49,250 --> 00:18:51,970
<Default><b>They must have wanted
to share something urgently.</b></Default>

472
00:18:52,940 --> 00:18:54,116
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
What's this?</b></Default>

473
00:18:54,140 --> 00:18:56,045
<Default><b>A dragon
emperor fragment.</b></Default>

474
00:18:56,069 --> 00:18:58,045
<Default><b>And it appears to contain
a direct message</b></Default>

475
00:18:58,069 --> 00:19:00,275
<Default><b>from the Water
Dragon itself.</b></Default>

476
00:19:00,299 --> 00:19:01,535
<Default><b>Are you sure about this?</b></Default>

477
00:19:01,559 --> 00:19:03,275
<Default><b>You might go out
of control again.</b></Default>

478
00:19:03,299 --> 00:19:04,835
<Default><b>[GAELION]
I sense no evil.</b></Default>

479
00:19:04,859 --> 00:19:05,976
<Default><b>It should be fine.</b></Default>

480
00:19:06,000 --> 00:19:07,825
<Default><b>[bright flourish]</b></Default>

481
00:19:07,849 --> 00:19:10,025
<Default><b>Hmm, I see.</b></Default>

482
00:19:10,049 --> 00:19:11,976
<Default><b>Did you learn
anything new?</b></Default>

483
00:19:12,000 --> 00:19:14,726
<Default><b>The Water Dragon wishes
for you to return this nation</b></Default>

484
00:19:14,750 --> 00:19:17,186
<Default><b>to its rightful form</b></Default>

485
00:19:17,210 --> 00:19:18,995
<Default><b>say anything
more than that.</b></Default>

486
00:19:19,019 --> 00:19:21,585
<Default><b>What do you mean
"rightful form"?</b></Default>

487
00:19:21,609 --> 00:19:22,976
<Default><b>[GAELION]
For many years</b></Default>

488
00:19:23,000 --> 00:19:25,765
<Default><b>this nation
was protected by a barrier.</b></Default>

489
00:19:25,789 --> 00:19:28,255
<Default><b>This barrier
existed to protect</b></Default>

490
00:19:28,279 --> 00:19:31,255
<Default><b>the Pacifier
of Spirit Implements.</b></Default>

491
00:19:31,279 --> 00:19:33,606
<Default><b>Oh, what do you
mean by "Pacifier"?</b></Default>

492
00:19:33,630 --> 00:19:36,035
<Default><b>[GAELION] I'm afraid I don't
have more information on it.</b></Default>

493
00:19:36,059 --> 00:19:37,976
<Default><b>But it seems
your clan fulfilled</b></Default>

494
00:19:38,000 --> 00:19:39,606
<Default><b>that role for
generations.</b></Default>

495
00:19:39,630 --> 00:19:40,946
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

496
00:19:40,970 --> 00:19:43,335
<Default><b>Hey, Raphtalia</b></Default>

497
00:19:43,359 --> 00:19:44,765
<Default><b>anything about
that to you?</b></Default>

498
00:19:44,789 --> 00:19:47,995
<Default><b>Never. I wish that I could
be of more help.</b></Default>

499
00:19:48,019 --> 00:19:49,815
<Default><b>He probably thought
it was something</b></Default>

500
00:19:49,839 --> 00:19:51,216
<Default><b>you didn't need to know.</b></Default>

501
00:19:51,240 --> 00:19:52,217
<Default><b>Yes.</b></Default>

502
00:19:52,241 --> 00:19:53,755
<Default><b>"Spirit implements."</b></Default>

503
00:19:53,779 --> 00:19:56,206
<Default><b>If I had to guess</b></Default>

504
00:19:56,230 --> 00:19:57,916
<Default><b>to the Cardinal Weapons.</b></Default>

505
00:19:57,940 --> 00:20:00,116
<Default><b>I was just thinking
the same thing.</b></Default>

506
00:20:00,140 --> 00:20:02,485
<Default><b>Then pacifier
must mean...</b></Default>

507
00:20:02,509 --> 00:20:04,936
<Default><b>Judging by the name</b></Default>

508
00:20:04,960 --> 00:20:08,295
<Default><b>who keeps a tight leash on
the wielders of those weapons.</b></Default>

509
00:20:08,319 --> 00:20:12,765
<Default><b>For example, if a hero
misuses the power of a weapon</b></Default>

510
00:20:12,789 --> 00:20:15,106
<Default><b>having somebody who's
immune to its effects</b></Default>

511
00:20:15,130 --> 00:20:17,490
<Default><b>would prevent the worst
from transpiring.</b></Default>

512
00:20:18,789 --> 00:20:20,565
<Default><b>The weapons they've
been using must</b></Default>

513
00:20:20,589 --> 00:20:22,706
<Default><b>be an application
of that art.</b></Default>

514
00:20:22,730 --> 00:20:24,530
<Default><b>[RAPHTALIA]
Master Naofumi?</b></Default>

515
00:20:25,329 --> 00:20:27,315
<Default><b>All right, Gaelion</b></Default>

516
00:20:27,339 --> 00:20:29,035
<Default><b>are we supposed
to do then?</b></Default>

517
00:20:29,059 --> 00:20:32,235
<Default><b>It's important to note
the emperor has control</b></Default>

518
00:20:32,259 --> 00:20:33,926
<Default><b>over Q'ten Lo's barrier.</b></Default>

519
00:20:33,950 --> 00:20:36,325
<Default><b>Our first order of business
should be to take care of that</b></Default>

520
00:20:36,349 --> 00:20:38,666
<Default><b>or our friends
can't make landfall.</b></Default>

521
00:20:38,690 --> 00:20:39,886
<Default><b>Seriously?</b></Default>

522
00:20:39,910 --> 00:20:41,035
<Default><b>Raphy?</b></Default>

523
00:20:41,059 --> 00:20:42,035
<Default><b>Raphy!</b></Default>

524
00:20:42,059 --> 00:20:43,036
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

525
00:20:43,060 --> 00:20:44,726
<Default><b>Raphy. Raphy.</b></Default>

526
00:20:44,750 --> 00:20:45,727
<Default><b>Raphy!</b></Default>

527
00:20:45,751 --> 00:20:48,106
<Default><b>Raphy. Raph-Raph.</b></Default>

528
00:20:48,130 --> 00:20:49,106
<Default><b>Raphy.</b></Default>

529
00:20:49,130 --> 00:20:50,107
<Default><b>Raphy!</b></Default>

530
00:20:50,131 --> 00:20:51,585
<Default><b>Whoa!</b></Default>

531
00:20:51,609 --> 00:20:53,345
<Default><b>- Raphy.
- Huh?</b></Default>

532
00:20:53,369 --> 00:20:55,906
<Default><b>I'm told they're stuck
going around in circles.</b></Default>

533
00:20:55,930 --> 00:20:57,696
<Default><b>They can't
go any further.</b></Default>

534
00:20:57,720 --> 00:20:59,916
<Default><b>It's just like
the Water Dragon said, huh?</b></Default>

535
00:20:59,940 --> 00:21:01,616
<Default><b>So even if
we'd kept going</b></Default>

536
00:21:01,640 --> 00:21:03,216
<Default><b>we never
would have made it, huh?</b></Default>

537
00:21:03,240 --> 00:21:05,376
<Default><b>It would appear
there's a base nearby</b></Default>

538
00:21:05,400 --> 00:21:07,186
<Default><b>that controls
the barrier.</b></Default>

539
00:21:07,210 --> 00:21:10,109
<Default><b>[footsteps]</b></Default>

540
00:21:15,450 --> 00:21:19,626
<Default><b>I hate the idea that this
thing is manipulating us</b></Default>

541
00:21:19,650 --> 00:21:21,490
<Default><b>but we don't
have a choice.</b></Default>

542
00:21:23,549 --> 00:21:24,845
<Default><b>[RAPHTALIA]
What's this?</b></Default>

543
00:21:24,869 --> 00:21:27,075
<Default><b>The Water Dragon
prepared these.</b></Default>

544
00:21:27,099 --> 00:21:29,765
<Default><b>You will have to wear them
to hide your identities.</b></Default>

545
00:21:29,789 --> 00:21:31,629
<Default><b>They're
well-prepared, huh?</b></Default>

546
00:21:32,789 --> 00:21:36,265
<Default><b>[calming music]</b></Default>

547
00:21:36,289 --> 00:21:39,666
<Default><b>[gasps] A shining
cherry tree?</b></Default>

548
00:21:39,690 --> 00:21:42,805
<Default><b>[SADEENA] The Sakura Lumina
are unique to Q'ten Lo.</b></Default>

549
00:21:42,829 --> 00:21:49,829
<Default><b>♪♪</b></Default>

550
00:21:50,349 --> 00:21:52,476
<Default><b>Well, it wasn't easy</b></Default>

551
00:21:52,500 --> 00:21:54,420
<Default><b>at least we all
made it here.</b></Default>

552
00:21:55,720 --> 00:21:57,976
<Default><b>This place</b></Default>

553
00:21:58,000 --> 00:21:59,785
<Default><b>and father
were both born.</b></Default>

554
00:21:59,809 --> 00:22:02,680
<Default><b>♪♪</b></Default>

555
00:22:05,079 --> 00:22:08,055
<Default><b>[singing in Japanese]</b></Default>

556
00:22:08,079 --> 00:22:15,079
<Default><b>♪♪</b></Default>

557
00:23:36,269 --> 00:23:39,269
<Default><b>ARRIVING IN Q'TEN LO</b></Default>

